'''不穿胸罩'''（{{lang-en|Braless}}）是指女性反對在上衣中再加上[[胸罩|胸罩]]，有一些千禧世代的女性支持此一作法<ref>{{cite web |last1=Mallenbaum |first1=Carly |title=Why Millennials are going braless |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2016/07/19/braless-millenials-bralette/87111292/ |website=USA TODAY |accessdate=20 September 2018 |language=en |date=July 19, 2016 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180920084248/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/2016/07/19/braless-millenials-bralette/87111292/ |archive-date=2018-09-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[女权主义|女权主义]]者中，这种穿戴方式带有女权解放的意义。某些人聲稱「长期穿戴胸罩会增加患上[[乳癌|乳癌]]的风险」<ref>{{cite web | language =中文 | publisher =北京新浪網 | title =女性每天戴胸罩超12小時患乳癌風險高 | url =http://dailynews.sina.com/bg/news/heh/sinacn/20090817/2050582800.html | author = | date =2009年8月17日 | accessdate =2011-05-18 | archive-date =2016-03-04 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160304115017/http://dailynews.sina.com/bg/news/heh/sinacn/20090817/2050582800.html }}</ref>，但这一说法并未受到科学研究的支持<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.cancer.org/cancer/breast-cancer/risk-and-prevention/disproven-or-controversial-breast-cancer-risk-factors.html |title=Disproven or Controversial Breast Cancer Risk Factors |accessdate=2017-09-04 |archive-date=2019-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508013536/https://www.cancer.org/cancer/breast-cancer/risk-and-prevention/disproven-or-controversial-breast-cancer-risk-factors.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。「睡覺時宜不穿胸罩」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://sm21.net/vegabc/more/jian4kang1/ga066.htm |title=睡覺時宜不穿胸罩 |accessdate=2011-07-06 |archive-date=2011-04-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110408020157/http://sm21.net/vegabc/more/jian4kang1/ga066.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，也是“不穿胸罩主义者”持有的理据。[[法國|法國]]很多女性不穿胸罩，她們認為比較時髦及舒適。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://big5.china.com.cn/chinese/WISI/242877.htm |title=巴黎女性為何不穿內衣褲？ |access-date=2011-05-22 |archive-date=2017-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904113229/http://big5.china.com.cn/chinese/WISI/242877.htm }}</ref><ref>[http://www.lanews.gov.cn/women/thin/jsf/2011/05/23/163114266361.html 保护乳房健康 给你4个理由不穿胸罩]{{dead link|date=2017年11月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

